# Phase 1: Smart Contact Management System ‚Äî Requirement Analysis, Architecture & Design

## Overview

Building an enterprise-grade Smart Contact Management System ‚Äî a full-stack SaaS platform combining **React 19 + TypeScript** frontend, **Node.js + Express + MongoDB** backend, and a **C++17 Algorithm Engine** for high-performance DSA operations (Trie search, merge sort, duplicate detection, etc.).

This phase covers requirement analysis, architecture decisions, database schema design, folder scaffolding, and documentation diagrams. **No application code is written in this phase** ‚Äî only the project skeleton and design documents.

