### 4. Architecture Decisions

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| **Monorepo** | Single repo, 3 independent apps | Simplifies development, CI/CD, and deployment. Each part can run independently. |
| **State Management** | Redux Toolkit | Centralized state for contacts, auth, UI. RTK Query for server state caching. |
| **API Communication** | REST + Axios + TanStack Query | REST is simpler than GraphQL for CRUD. TanStack Query handles caching, refetching, pagination. |
| **Auth** | JWT (access + refresh tokens) | Stateless auth. Access token (15min) + refresh token (7d) for security. |
| **C++ Bridge** | child_process spawn | No native addons needed. C++ binary is standalone. Language-agnostic protocol via JSON over stdio. |
| **File Uploads** | Multer ‚Üí Cloudinary | Multer handles multipart parsing. Cloudinary provides CDN-backed image hosting with transformations. |
| **Soft Deletes** | `isDeleted` flag + `deletedAt` | Enables undo/restore. Trash can feature. Permanent delete after 30 days. |
| **Real-time** | Socket.io | Live updates when contacts are modified (multi-tab/device sync). |
| **Dark Mode** | CSS variables + React context | Theme toggle with system preference detection. No flash of unstyled content. |

